{
  "video_id": "QMcwDmHiUZ8",
  "title": "A new way to fund health care for the most vulnerable | Andrew Bastawrous",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13785.0,
      "end_time": 17559.0,
      "text": "These two Kenyan ladies were best friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17583.0,
      "end_time": 19487.0,
      "text": "from neighboring villages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19511.0,
      "end_time": 23284.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;d stopped seeing each other, literally, for 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23308.0,
      "end_time": 27330.0,
      "text": "because both had gone blind from a curable condition called cataracts."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27778.0,
      "end_time": 30857.0,
      "text": "They hadn&#39;t been aware they&#39;d been sat together for over an hour"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30881.0,
      "end_time": 33612.0,
      "text": "when we offered them surgery at the nearest hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33636.0,
      "end_time": 35782.0,
      "text": "Mama Jane, on the right, told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35806.0,
      "end_time": 39430.0,
      "text": "her biggest fear was that she would poison her grandson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39670.0,
      "end_time": 40865.0,
      "text": "whom she&#39;d never seen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40889.0,
      "end_time": 43743.0,
      "text": "because she couldn&#39;t see what she was cooking for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43767.0,
      "end_time": 47582.0,
      "text": "Her arms were covered in burns from cooking on a charcoal stove,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47606.0,
      "end_time": 51710.0,
      "text": "and she despaired that she was robbing her six-year-old grandson of his childhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51734.0,
      "end_time": 54113.0,
      "text": "because he was effectively her eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55240.0,
      "end_time": 59580.0,
      "text": "The effect of her blindness was going through the generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59820.0,
      "end_time": 62595.0,
      "text": "He wasn&#39;t able to go to school or break the cycle of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63262.0,
      "end_time": 66878.0,
      "text": "All of this, despite cost-effective solutions existing."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66902.0,
      "end_time": 69741.0,
      "text": "Cataract surgery can be done in under 10 minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69765.0,
      "end_time": 71558.0,
      "text": "for just a hundred dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71582.0,
      "end_time": 75640.0,
      "text": "Four in every five people who are blind don&#39;t need to be;"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75880.0,
      "end_time": 78280.0,
      "text": "curative or preventive treatments already exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79108.0,
      "end_time": 81561.0,
      "text": "Fortunately for Mama Jane and her friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81585.0,
      "end_time": 83411.0,
      "text": "a donor had provided treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83436.0,
      "end_time": 85770.0,
      "text": "so that we could take them to the nearest hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85794.0,
      "end_time": 87338.0,
      "text": "three hours away."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87362.0,
      "end_time": 89175.0,
      "text": "But in that very same clinic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89200.0,
      "end_time": 90875.0,
      "text": "I met Theresa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90899.0,
      "end_time": 93986.0,
      "text": "a shy young woman who couldn&#39;t look me in the eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94100.0,
      "end_time": 95891.0,
      "text": "not because she couldn&#39;t see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95915.0,
      "end_time": 99690.0,
      "text": "but the appearance of the growth on her eyes called pterygium"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99930.0,
      "end_time": 100868.0,
      "text": "meant she&#39;d lost her confidence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100892.0,
      "end_time": 103258.0,
      "text": "and with it, her place in her community."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 103282.0,
      "end_time": 105838.0,
      "text": "She had no prospects for marriage or children"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105862.0,
      "end_time": 107895.0,
      "text": "and had been completely ostracized."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108381.0,
      "end_time": 111523.0,
      "text": "I knew how to treat her condition; it was pretty straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111547.0,
      "end_time": 114292.0,
      "text": "But we had strict instructions that the funds we had"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114316.0,
      "end_time": 115945.0,
      "text": "were for people with cataracts."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116945.0,
      "end_time": 118841.0,
      "text": "What was I supposed to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118865.0,
      "end_time": 120238.0,
      "text": "Ignore her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121710.0,
      "end_time": 124196.0,
      "text": "My wife and I managed to raise the funds to cover her treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124220.0,
      "end_time": 127510.0,
      "text": "but situations like Theresa were common every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127760.0,
      "end_time": 129579.0,
      "text": "where people had the wrong diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130680.0,
      "end_time": 131663.0,
      "text": "And by the \"wrong diseases,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131687.0,
      "end_time": 135597.0,
      "text": "I mean conditions for which funding hadn&#39;t been earmarked."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137550.0,
      "end_time": 141449.0,
      "text": "Earmarking may seem like smart business or smart philanthropy on paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141473.0,
      "end_time": 144955.0,
      "text": "but it doesn&#39;t make any sense when you&#39;re looking the person in the eye."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144979.0,
      "end_time": 149805.0,
      "text": "Yet, this is how we deliver health care to millions of people the world over."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151513.0,
      "end_time": 154743.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been thinking about this problem for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155466.0,
      "end_time": 159815.0,
      "text": "Things happened to me at the age of 12 that completely transformed my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159839.0,
      "end_time": 163256.0,
      "text": "My teachers insisted that I would go for an eye test."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163280.0,
      "end_time": 165339.0,
      "text": "I resisted it for as many years as I could"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165363.0,
      "end_time": 167575.0,
      "text": "because as the only brown boy in the school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167599.0,
      "end_time": 170423.0,
      "text": "I already felt like a chocolate chip in rice pudding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170448.0,
      "end_time": 174423.0,
      "text": "and the idea of looking more different was not particularly appealing."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174447.0,
      "end_time": 177110.0,
      "text": "You see, I&#39;d associated an eye test with wearing glasses"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177134.0,
      "end_time": 178506.0,
      "text": "and looking different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178531.0,
      "end_time": 180113.0,
      "text": "not with seeing differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 180708.0,
      "end_time": 182846.0,
      "text": "When eventually I was persuaded to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182870.0,
      "end_time": 185218.0,
      "text": "the optometrist fitted me with the trial lenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185242.0,
      "end_time": 187989.0,
      "text": "and was shocked at just how poor my sight was."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188140.0,
      "end_time": 190642.0,
      "text": "He sent me outside to report what I could see."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190666.0,
      "end_time": 195474.0,
      "text": "I remember looking up and seeing trees had leaves on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195498.0,
      "end_time": 197179.0,
      "text": "I had never known this."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198680.0,
      "end_time": 202980.0,
      "text": "Later that week, for the first time, I saw stars in the night sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202122.0,
      "end_time": 203561.0,
      "text": "It was breathtaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 204163.0,
      "end_time": 207500.0,
      "text": "In fact, the entire trajectory of my life changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 207524.0,
      "end_time": 211890.0,
      "text": "I went from a failing child at school who was constantly told I was lazy"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211113.0,
      "end_time": 212328.0,
      "text": "and not paying attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212352.0,
      "end_time": 215308.0,
      "text": "to suddenly being a child with opportunity and potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216340.0,
      "end_time": 219698.0,
      "text": "But I soon realized that this opportunity was not universal."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219722.0,
      "end_time": 221615.0,
      "text": "That same summer, in Egypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 221639.0,
      "end_time": 223947.0,
      "text": "the home where my parents are originally from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 223971.0,
      "end_time": 226734.0,
      "text": "I was with children that looked a lot more like me"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226758.0,
      "end_time": 228950.0,
      "text": "but couldn&#39;t have been more different."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228974.0,
      "end_time": 231650.0,
      "text": "What separated us was opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 231740.0,
      "end_time": 234938.0,
      "text": "How is it that I had this life and they had theirs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 234962.0,
      "end_time": 236786.0,
      "text": "It still makes no sense to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 237306.0,
      "end_time": 238465.0,
      "text": "How is it we&#39;ve --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 238489.0,
      "end_time": 242200.0,
      "text": "in a world where glasses, that completely changed my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242224.0,
      "end_time": 244533.0,
      "text": "have been around for 700 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 244557.0,
      "end_time": 247908.0,
      "text": "yet two and a half billion people still can&#39;t access them."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 248503.0,
      "end_time": 252174.0,
      "text": "This deep sense of injustice drove me to become a doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252199.0,
      "end_time": 253876.0,
      "text": "eventually an eye surgeon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 253900.0,
      "end_time": 258430.0,
      "text": "and in 2012, my wife and I packed our bags and moved to Kenya"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258454.0,
      "end_time": 260850.0,
      "text": "to try and give something back."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 260797.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263820.0,
      "text": "We started by setting up a hundred eye clinics"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263106.0,
      "end_time": 264553.0,
      "text": "across the Great Rift Valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 264577.0,
      "end_time": 267820.0,
      "text": "where we met people like Mama Jane and Theresa."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 267855.0,
      "end_time": 270353.0,
      "text": "We founded a new organization called Peek Vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270377.0,
      "end_time": 274500.0,
      "text": "a social enterprise where we built smartphone technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274290.0,
      "end_time": 276626.0,
      "text": "that makes it possible for people in the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276650.0,
      "end_time": 278376.0,
      "text": "to find people in their homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 278401.0,
      "end_time": 281960.0,
      "text": "the most vulnerable groups who are being missed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 281120.0,
      "end_time": 283965.0,
      "text": "and created new tools that made it easier to diagnose them"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283989.0,
      "end_time": 285837.0,
      "text": "and connect them to services."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 285862.0,
      "end_time": 288158.0,
      "text": "Inspired by the challenges I&#39;d had as a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288182.0,
      "end_time": 291740.0,
      "text": "we equipped teachers, 25 of them, with smartphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 291980.0,
      "end_time": 292965.0,
      "text": "to screen children in schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 292989.0,
      "end_time": 295387.0,
      "text": "Our first program resulted in 21,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 295411.0,
      "end_time": 297563.0,
      "text": "being screened in just nine days."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 298149.0,
      "end_time": 301569.0,
      "text": "That same program was replicated to reach 200,000 children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 301593.0,
      "end_time": 303438.0,
      "text": "covering the entire district."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 303462.0,
      "end_time": 306310.0,
      "text": "Soon we were able to repeat this in six new programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306550.0,
      "end_time": 307405.0,
      "text": "in different countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 308106.0,
      "end_time": 312240.0,
      "text": "But now, I was faced with the very same problems I had with Theresa"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 312480.0,
      "end_time": 313836.0,
      "text": "of earmarked funds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 313860.0,
      "end_time": 315659.0,
      "text": "but now as an organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 316374.0,
      "end_time": 319770.0,
      "text": "People wanted to fund specific projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 319794.0,
      "end_time": 321549.0,
      "text": "or particular diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 321573.0,
      "end_time": 323512.0,
      "text": "or subsets of the population."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 324178.0,
      "end_time": 325773.0,
      "text": "But it didn&#39;t make sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 325797.0,
      "end_time": 328477.0,
      "text": "because what we needed to do was build an incredible team"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 328501.0,
      "end_time": 331214.0,
      "text": "who could create the systems that would change the lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 331238.0,
      "end_time": 333633.0,
      "text": "of millions of people, whatever their needs were."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 334385.0,
      "end_time": 335880.0,
      "text": "But it didn&#39;t work that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 338166.0,
      "end_time": 343189.0,
      "text": "Soon, we were able to align ourselves with partners who understood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 343213.0,
      "end_time": 345270.0,
      "text": "because I understand the challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 345294.0,
      "end_time": 348568.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, you need to trust where your money&#39;s going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 348593.0,
      "end_time": 351213.0,
      "text": "and that trust usually manifests through the requirement"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 351237.0,
      "end_time": 353688.0,
      "text": "to create detailed plans -- lots of paperwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 353712.0,
      "end_time": 356510.0,
      "text": "But what happens if the dynamic needs of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 356760.0,
      "end_time": 358118.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t fit with the plan that you created,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 358142.0,
      "end_time": 361700.0,
      "text": "and your funding is dependent on delivering the plan?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 361950.0,
      "end_time": 362547.0,
      "text": "You end up with a choice:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 363790.0,
      "end_time": 365563.0,
      "text": "Do you serve the plan, the funder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365587.0,
      "end_time": 366998.0,
      "text": "or do you serve the need?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 367482.0,
      "end_time": 369909.0,
      "text": "This is not a choice we should have to make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 369933.0,
      "end_time": 372994.0,
      "text": "because ultimately, we can only serve one master."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374633.0,
      "end_time": 376740.0,
      "text": "The measure of our humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 376764.0,
      "end_time": 379601.0,
      "text": "is how we serve the most vulnerable amongst us."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 380330.0,
      "end_time": 384495.0,
      "text": "Currently, the system is not working, and too many people are being left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 385245.0,
      "end_time": 388718.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been fortunate to find incredible supporters and partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 388742.0,
      "end_time": 391512.0,
      "text": "which led to a new program in Botswana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 391536.0,
      "end_time": 394878.0,
      "text": "in which every single schoolchild is being screened and treated"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 394902.0,
      "end_time": 397256.0,
      "text": "by the end of 2021,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 397280.0,
      "end_time": 399344.0,
      "text": "meaning an entire generation of children"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 399368.0,
      "end_time": 401849.0,
      "text": "will have the opportunity that good vision affords."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 402423.0,
      "end_time": 404502.0,
      "text": "But this took years of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 404526.0,
      "end_time": 406620.0,
      "text": "It took multiple feasibility studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 406644.0,
      "end_time": 409238.0,
      "text": "engaging different partners and stakeholders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 409262.0,
      "end_time": 411524.0,
      "text": "business cases, economic analyses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 411548.0,
      "end_time": 414341.0,
      "text": "to persuade the government to eventually come on board."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 414365.0,
      "end_time": 418281.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re now leading and funding this in their own national budget."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 418305.0,
      "end_time": 421524.0,
      "text": "But we did not have the resources to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 421937.0,
      "end_time": 425317.0,
      "text": "Our visionary funders and partners came alongside us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 425341.0,
      "end_time": 428666.0,
      "text": "and the key ingredients were we were aligned on mission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 428690.0,
      "end_time": 430319.0,
      "text": "on the why we were doing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 431710.0,
      "end_time": 434871.0,
      "text": "We agreed on the outcome, what had to be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 434895.0,
      "end_time": 438931.0,
      "text": "But critically, they were flexible and gave us autonomy"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 438956.0,
      "end_time": 441204.0,
      "text": "to work out how we got there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 441228.0,
      "end_time": 445204.0,
      "text": "giving us the space to be creative, ambitious and take risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 445795.0,
      "end_time": 448159.0,
      "text": "What if all health care looked like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 448183.0,
      "end_time": 452279.0,
      "text": "What would it mean for all the social causes we&#39;re trying to solve?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 453171.0,
      "end_time": 454837.0,
      "text": "Business knows this."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 454862.0,
      "end_time": 457441.0,
      "text": "By taking a long-term, ambitious view"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 457465.0,
      "end_time": 459744.0,
      "text": "and giving people the autonomy to be creative"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 459768.0,
      "end_time": 461775.0,
      "text": "to solve our world&#39;s biggest challenges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 461800.0,
      "end_time": 463872.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve disrupted entire industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 463896.0,
      "end_time": 466470.0,
      "text": "Look at Amazon, Google."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 466710.0,
      "end_time": 468202.0,
      "text": "Surely, we need the same level of ambition"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 468226.0,
      "end_time": 471193.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;re going to serve the most vulnerable in our societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 471574.0,
      "end_time": 473918.0,
      "text": "As a planet, we&#39;ve set a target,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 473942.0,
      "end_time": 476338.0,
      "text": "the Sustainable Development Goals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 476362.0,
      "end_time": 480493.0,
      "text": "yet we&#39;re spending less than half the amount on tackling the global goals"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 480517.0,
      "end_time": 482452.0,
      "text": "than we are on conflict resolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 482476.0,
      "end_time": 486172.0,
      "text": "which mostly arises from the very inequalities we&#39;re not serving."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 487140.0,
      "end_time": 488568.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s time for change."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 489150.0,
      "end_time": 492747.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just common sense as well -- it makes business sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 492771.0,
      "end_time": 494532.0,
      "text": "Our work in Botswana showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 494556.0,
      "end_time": 498476.0,
      "text": "for a modest investment, the economy would gain 1.3 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498500.0,
      "end_time": 500364.0,
      "text": "over the lifetime of the children."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 500388.0,
      "end_time": 503850.0,
      "text": "That was 150 times return on investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 503681.0,
      "end_time": 507229.0,
      "text": "But part of the problem is that value is generated in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 507254.0,
      "end_time": 509247.0,
      "text": "but we need the money now to deliver it."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 510424.0,
      "end_time": 512775.0,
      "text": "Turns out, this is not a new problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 512799.0,
      "end_time": 515310.0,
      "text": "Banks have been solving it for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 515559.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517259.99999999994,
      "text": "Simply put, it&#39;s called financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 518192.0,
      "end_time": 519528.0,
      "text": "If you want to buy a house"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 519552.0,
      "end_time": 521918.0,
      "text": "but you can&#39;t afford to pay for it up front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 521942.0,
      "end_time": 525313.0,
      "text": "the bank financiers, you see, can realize that future value now."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 525337.0,
      "end_time": 528345.0,
      "text": "In other words, you can live in the house straightaway."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 528369.0,
      "end_time": 529624.0,
      "text": "But what if you couldn&#39;t?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 529648.0,
      "end_time": 533750.0,
      "text": "What if you had to wait until you&#39;d raised all of the money to move into the house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 533774.0,
      "end_time": 536564.0,
      "text": "and you were kept homeless whilst trying to save the money"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 536588.0,
      "end_time": 538135.0,
      "text": "to get there in the first place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 538159.0,
      "end_time": 541860.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d end up in an impossible cycle, never able to get there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 541110.0,
      "end_time": 543893.0,
      "text": "yet that&#39;s this very same bind we&#39;ve put on ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 544694.0,
      "end_time": 546666.0,
      "text": "Inspired by the change in Botswana"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 546691.0,
      "end_time": 549645.0,
      "text": "and by the visionary support of our funders and partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 549669.0,
      "end_time": 552540.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve come together -- two world-leading banks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 552565.0,
      "end_time": 555932.0,
      "text": "for-profit and private, not-for-profit organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 555956.0,
      "end_time": 557830.0,
      "text": "foundations and philanthropists --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 557854.0,
      "end_time": 560273.0,
      "text": "to launch the Vision Catalyst Fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 560297.0,
      "end_time": 563340.0,
      "text": "a fund which will have trust built in by design."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 563693.0,
      "end_time": 566240.0,
      "text": "It will make funding available now"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 566264.0,
      "end_time": 570127.0,
      "text": "to the organizations that can serve the need of the most vulnerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 570151.0,
      "end_time": 574650.0,
      "text": "It will ensure that those organizations can work together in partnership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 574900.0,
      "end_time": 576526.0,
      "text": "rather than competing for limited funds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 576550.0,
      "end_time": 579353.0,
      "text": "serving the priority needs of an entire population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 579377.0,
      "end_time": 580909.0,
      "text": "whatever they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 580933.0,
      "end_time": 583452.0,
      "text": "so that ultimately the individuals affected"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 583476.0,
      "end_time": 585723.0,
      "text": "can receive the care that they deserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 586176.0,
      "end_time": 587878.0,
      "text": "And as we&#39;ve shown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 587902.0,
      "end_time": 590641.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t make just a health and social difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 590665.0,
      "end_time": 593450.0,
      "text": "it creates huge economic benefit."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 593700.0,
      "end_time": 595935.0,
      "text": "This benefit in itself will create sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 595959.0,
      "end_time": 601103.0,
      "text": "to perpetuate a virtuous, catalytic cycle of improvement and change."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 601749.0,
      "end_time": 603619.0,
      "text": "Because when we do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 603643.0,
      "end_time": 606912.0,
      "text": "the individual needs of people like myself can be met."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 607979.0,
      "end_time": 612138.0,
      "text": "And this coalition has come together this year"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 612162.0,
      "end_time": 614950.0,
      "text": "to make a commitment with 53 heads of government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 614974.0,
      "end_time": 617160.0,
      "text": "who have now committed to take action"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 617400.0,
      "end_time": 619928.0,
      "text": "towards achieving access to quality eye care for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 620417.0,
      "end_time": 622186.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve had incredible commitments"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 622210.0,
      "end_time": 625700.0,
      "text": "of 200 million pairs of glasses to the fund"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 625310.0,
      "end_time": 626704.0,
      "text": "and millions of dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 627807.0,
      "end_time": 630952.0,
      "text": "so that the dynamic and individual needs of people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 630976.0,
      "end_time": 633527.0,
      "text": "like my own issues that I had as child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 633551.0,
      "end_time": 636533.0,
      "text": "and like Theresa, who just required simple surgery --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 636557.0,
      "end_time": 637884.0,
      "text": "can be met."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 638475.0,
      "end_time": 642477.0,
      "text": "For Theresa, it meant her place back in society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 642501.0,
      "end_time": 644919.0,
      "text": "now with her own family and children."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 645506.0,
      "end_time": 650156.0,
      "text": "And for Mama Jane, it wasn&#39;t just restoring her sight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 650181.0,
      "end_time": 653185.0,
      "text": "it meant the opportunity to restore hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 653209.0,
      "end_time": 654978.0,
      "text": "to restore joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 655200.0,
      "end_time": 656780.0,
      "text": "and to restore dignity."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 657457.0,
      "end_time": 663141.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 669230.0,
      "end_time": 670429.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 670453.0,
      "end_time": 673670.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}